cards: Pickup shirt, name tag, and bag
Head to LEINA where you can pick up your shirt, nametag, and bag.
Get keys and check in with medicine
Go pick up your keys and check in with medicine at LEINA
Find your room and move in
Go find your room and get it all set up! The QR code for this box can be found in the hallways near your room.
Find the Grove
Become acquainted with the Grove, this is the location you will be ending at.

Find a friend in your region
You better not lie about this one... Go make a friend with somebody in the same region as you.
Find a friend in your grade
Tired of making friends? Well too bad. Go make a friend with somebody who is in the same grade as you.
Say thanks to support staff or tech crew
These guy work way too hard, go give them your appreciation.
